OL,4,Cfootballer harassed former partner
OL,6,FA former Premier League footballer who
OL,7,Fharassed his ex-girlfriend by calling
OL,8,Fand emailing her from multiple
OL,9,Faccounts and numbers has been given a
OL,10,Frestraining order.
OL,12,FColin Hendry, 59, harassed his victim
OL,13,Ffor six weeks after their relationship
OL,14,Fended in 2024, using No Caller ID when
OL,15,Fhis number was blocked, before
OL,16,Fcreating multiple email accounts, and
OL,17,Fmessaging her on LinkedIn.
