OL,6,F"This outcome is a clear indication
OL,7,Fthat the CPS will not hesitate to
OL,8,Fprosecute anyone guilty of harassment
OL,9,Fwhether this is in person or online."
OL,11,FThe victim told police Hendry's
OL,12,Fbehaviour made her feel "depressed and
OL,13,Fanxious", she feared an unannounced
OL,14,Fvisit from him every time she left the
OL,15,Fhouse.
OL,17,FShe said he consistently attempted to
OL,18,Fcontact her, showing up at her house
OL,19,Fwith unwanted gifts and flowers.
