OL,6,FLancashire Police contacted the former
OL,7,FScotland international to warn him
OL,8,Fabout his behaviour, telling him to
OL,9,Fcease all contact with his ex-partner.
OL,11,FBut, although Hendry admitted to his
OL,12,Fconduct he denied harassment, claiming
OL,13,Fhe never received a written warning
OL,14,Ffrom police so continued to contact
OL,15,Fher out of "concern" for the victim
OL,16,Fand her dog.
OL,18,FHe later admitted one count of
OL,19,Fharassment without violence.
